title: First Aid Kit Interprets Leonard Cohen with Friends 2016
description: When Leonard Cohen passed away in November 2016, the First Aid Kit sisters Klara and Johanna Söderberg decided to make a tribute concert for their idol. They invited a number of Swedish artists and actors to interpret the Canadian singer and poet in word and tone. It became a peculiar and refined performance at the Royal Dramatic Theater large scene. We hear actors Maia Hansson Bergqvist and Nina Zanjani, who also directed the performance. And the artists Frida Hyvönen, Annika Norlin, Emil "Loney Dear" The Swan, Maja Francis and Jesper Lindell offer their own versions of songs from Cohen's rich production. Original demuxed from 720p video of concert that is/were available on SVT Play for Swedish citizens.
